data.description: Check out this amazing townhome nestled within the highly sought-after 85212 zip! The list of upgrades is extensive. Beautiful tile floor, custom plantation shutters, water softener, oversized 2 car garage and accent walls throughout. Open and airy ambiance. Chef's kitchen features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, self-closing cabinetry, tiled backsplash, RO system, kitchen bar and upgraded fixtures. Master bathroom has barn doors, double sinks. Spacious 2nd floor living area/den AND 3rd floor den. Master has its own floor with private balcony. Bathrooms conveniently located on each floor. Home comes complete with Smart home features including Ring Security System and Nest Thermostats. Steps to community pool!
